  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "Using the encoded heuristics, the labeling functions make predictions as to which label a clinical note should be assigned.",
    "Predictions from these labeling functions are then combined to develop a generative labeler model.",
    "We used the Snorkel framework [16] to implement data programming.",
    "A preprocessing framework [17] was applied to our notes to split them into sentences using the spaCy [18] framework, with a specialized tokenizer to recognize terms specific to medical literature.",
    "Thus parsed grammatical information was made available to the labeling functions as metadata.We then used the development set to understand how the AF prediagnosis was described, and we expressed each pattern as a labeling function."
  ],
